</font></b><p><b><font size="4">by M. E. (Pete) Thompson
<br>and Rick Obermeyer 
</font></b></p><p><b><font size="4"><i>in 19th Century Seminole Mens Clothing</i>
<br><a href="http://www.nativetech.org/seminole/obermeyer.html">
Rick Obermeyer ~ Editor</a>
</font></b></p><p><b><font size="4"><font size="5">PATTERN &amp; CONSTRUCTION</font></font></b></p></center>
</td></tr></tbody></table>
